943&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71fe7308cf7aec2536740f7409989df9aa625858","tid":1517854,"uid":247699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=351e8b81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d217b73c34a2601695c7d818f63c0472c5c1f005","tid":1517854,"uid":181703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"大把人仲驚緊<br />\n我只係想講我地香港人已經冇得驚"},{"pid":"65c742a61cee5c005b863cbbbb18eff6b7931281","tid":1517854,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8cb6abe98ef6800d1af44838d010b6919a966ee","tid":1517854,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0e89cd42ad87b5996c146169be7b261ab2eab96","tid":1517854,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"攬炒係咩？"},{"pid":"0342cc5a8f72326376b25dc9a3e2ea0fe9